text: Hi everyone, I want to keep your calendars up to date. There will be no Finance Pro-Sem this coming Friday, the 13th. On the 20th, our Pro-Sem time will be adjusted for the Homecoming Schedule. We will have an interactive Finance Pro-Sem alongside alumni taking part in the MBA Multi-Year Alumni Reunion that day. The Pro-Sem will be from 1-2:30pm on the 20th. Room to be determined. Enjoy the rest of your weekend!
